The algorithms in this software are described in

  Timo Baumann and David Schlangen (2011).
  "Predicting the Micro-Timing of User Input for an Incremental 
  Spoken Dialogue System that Completes a User's Ongoing Turn".
  in Proceedings of SIGDial, Portland, USA.

For your convenience, a bibtex entry for the paper is given below:

